## Quick start

```bash
npm install          # install dependencies
cp .env.example .env # fill in any credentials
npm run build        # compile TypeScript to dist/

# Local (stdio) — what most desktop AI clients launch:
MCPGEN_TRANSPORT=stdio node dist/server.js

# Remote (Streamable HTTP) — POST /mcp on port 3000:
MCPGEN_TRANSPORT=http node dist/server.js
```

